<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>URL Not Found - URL Shortener</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/error.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="mask-icon" href="/favicon.svg" color="#667eea">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="background-shapes">
        <div class="shape"></div>
        <div class="shape"></div>
        <div class="shape"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-icon">🔍</div>
        <h1>Short URL Not Found</h1>
        <p>
            The short URL <span class="short-id"><%= shortId %></span> does not exist in our system.
        </p>
        
        <div class="suggestions">
            <h3>💡 What you can do:</h3>
            <div class="suggestion-item">✓ Double-check the URL for typos</div>
            <div class="suggestion-item">✓ Make sure you copied the complete link</div>
            <div class="suggestion-item">✓ Create a new short URL if needed</div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/" class="home-link">
            <span>🏠</span>
            <span>Back to Home</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
